(1, 224, 217, 'Rice Breeder Scientist', '2024', 'sent', '2024-12-03 08:51:26.163', '2024-12-03 08:51:26.163', 'He is very effective in carrying out his activities.', 5, 'Technically, he is very competent for all the tasks assigned to him in 2024.', 5, 'He is  committed to the breeding unit and contributed significantly.', 4, 'He takes  initiatives to move the work forward in given time line.', 4, 'He followed very well the instructions and SOPs for all the breeding activities done.', 4, NULL, NULL, 'Mr Isaac Tawiah  has performed exceptionally  in all his assigned task in 2024.\n\n', 5, 'sent', 'I efficiently contributed to the overall performance of Crossing block and RGA activities ', 'Fully accustomed with the technical and work procedures and protocols used in the Crossing block and RGA Facilities ', 'Very committed to duties and completed them on time', 'I take the initiative to identify and pursue new tasks independently', 'Followed instructions with care and attention in delivering my duties', NULL, 'Collaboration with colleagues and support from leadership played a vital role in achieving my set objectives. I am grateful for the insights and encouragement from my team. I look forward to continuing to contribute to '),
(2, 4, 93, 'System Agronomist', '2024', 'sent', '2024-12-03 11:18:48.112', '2024-12-03 11:18:48.112', 'Much appreciated for completing the planned and additional activities.', 5, 'Well done. Much appreciated', 5, 'Mr Kokou is very committed to his work. Much appreciated.', 5, 'I agree with the comments of Mr Kokou. Well done.', 5, 'I agree with the self-evaluation', 4, 'I agree. Well done', 4, 'Thank you for all your achievement this year at AfricaRice. ', 5, 'sent', 'I am usually and all the times trying my best and do good job as per my assignments once my work plan is approved by my Supervisor. I have achieved all my objectives assigned across the West Africa countries and even the ones which are not included at the beguining of year. I am usually having a good relationship with my direct supervisors and others involved in lines of our activities', 'I have technical competency to implement my assigned works especially in agronomy research and development. This year I have conducted only development activities to train partners on RiceAdvice and RiceAdvice Lite validation trials and its dissemination in listed countries in my achievement. I have also trained the partmners on GAPfinder (SRP) benchmarking surveys. All these activities have been conducted under a minimum supervision', 'I was really committed for my assigned tasks for this year to complete them all under my supervisors minimum supervisoin', 'I have taken initiative this year especially in RiceAdvice to be appeared it again on Google Play Sotre to allow our partners to easily access it for their use. I usually take initiative to plan everything earlier to avoid any delay in work with partners', 'I have followed all instructions provided by my supervisors and others involved in our works and carry out and deliver the good and reliable results (outputs) as assigned in my work plan', 'I am providing instructions and supervise our field research asistants staff in Nigeria and also the work team from partners in different countries through our partners for good achievements of our technologies validation and its dissemination', 'In this year, our field activities implementation in different countries with our partners have been well carried out and good and reliable results have been achieved for some and some are still on-going and will be collected in early next year'),
(3, 121, 93, 'System Agronomist', '2024', 'sent', '2024-12-03 12:13:10.266', '2024-12-03 12:13:10.266', 'Ok. Agree', 4, 'Ok. Agree', 5, 'Ok. Agree', 4, 'Ok. Agree', 5, 'Ok. Agree', 4, 'OK. However you can take leadership roles in managing interns, research technicians.', 4, 'Ok. I agree with the comments of Perpetue Koume. Good luck with the work in the coming months', 4, 'sent', 'All requests and activities wear carried out efficiently.', 'No lack of skills to carry out the assigned duties.', 'I am fully committed to the institution by doing all my activities.', 'I don\'t wait to be reminded on what I have to do before doing it.', 'I respect all procedural rules in carrying out my activities.', 'Not Applicable', 'On the whole, all the assigned duties and scheduled activities were well achieved.   '),
(4, 80, 60, 'Agricultural Specialist For Climate Change', '2024', 'sent', '2024-12-03 13:40:00.593', '2024-12-03 13:40:00.593', 'All the priority objectives were achieved, which iis excellent. ', 5, 'The staff has all the required technical qualifications and is doing the analysis using internationally recognized standards. This needs to be encouraged. ', 5, 'The staff is highly committed to deliver good quality work and results from the laboratory have been satisfactory. ', 5, 'Great initiatives were taken to ensure timely availability of chemicals and qualified technicians to ensure the quality of the results. ', 5, 'The staff has diligently followed all rules and regulations, which is commendable. ', 5, 'Great leadership skills with the recruitment and capacity building of new research technician, and adequate supervision of field technicians and daily workers, which ensures field experiments and lab manipulations are conducted successfully. ', 5, 'Overall, the staff has been outstanding delivering effectively on all objectives, with demonstrated high technical skills, highly committed and great capacity of taking initiatives. ', 5, 'sent', 'We had been effective during 2024 to do well all our activities for the good operation of our program', 'We had great technical skills in managing laboratory activities and field trials, but despite this we are also improving our skills to be more comprehensive and useful to the program.', 'We had a strong commitment to the successful success of AfricaRice activities', 'Often, we take initiatives that are much appreciated by the supervisor', 'We follow the instructions and procedures requested by our supervisor', 'The supervision of my team in the laboratory and in the field is going very well', 'For this year 2024 we had achieved our goals that we have set.\nWe will work to be better next year.\n'),
