(12, 16, 73, 'Sustainable Productivity Enhancement Program Leader- Crop Ecophysiologist', '2024', 'draft', '2024-12-05 13:01:13.142', '2024-12-05 13:01:13.142', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'sent', 'I am efficient as a research assistant thanks to my 4 years of experience in this position.', 'I have the technical skills required as an agronomist to successfully carry out our activities. However, I continue to improve by learning new skills and seeking training opportunities for capacity development.', 'I am highly committed to my work and the tasks assigned to me.', 'I take initiative when required  particularly for activities under my supervision.', 'I always follow instructions and procedures to ensure activities run smoothly.', 'Leadership is essential for effective collaboration with diverse groups of people. For activities I am primarily responsible for, I do the best to lead the team effectively to achieve the objectives.', 'I have good technical skills as a research assistant and try my best to deliver on time. However, I feel I need to keep improving my skills to perform better especially in areas like manuscript writing, data analysis, and other important research skills.'),
(13, 175, 93, 'System Agronomist', '2024', 'sent', '2024-12-05 14:14:39.576', '2024-12-05 14:14:39.576', 'Ok. Agree. Yes, you have to do the work at a faster phase.', 4, 'OK. Agree. No issues with technical competencies. But you can keep on learning.', 4, 'Ok. Agree', 5, 'Ok. Agree. I appreciate your commitment towards the work planning and execution.', 5, 'Ok. Agree', 4, 'Well done', 5, 'Sophie did well in accomplishing the rice agronomy work in Madagascar, mainly to the BRECOMA work. Need to improve on data management, analytics and delivering research results timely. Based on her performance, I give a rating of 4 for the year 2024.', 4, 'sent', 'I am efficient in my work but I still have to improve in term of time management. ', 'I have the technical level required to manage the activities I lead as a research assistant.I continue to develop my technical skills.', 'I am very committed to perform the tasks assigned to me. ', 'I take ownership of my actions, whether by leading projects, proposing innovative solutions, or providing support to my colleagues.', 'Instructions and procedures were well followed as much as possible. ', 'I completed leadership courses through the AWARD Leadership Program this year and earned a certificate. I make a conscious effort to apply the leadership skills I gained from the program in every situation I encounter.', 'At times, my desire to deliver high-quality work has led to missing deadlines. However, this year has helped me recognize the importance of balancing quality with timely delivery. I have come to understand that meeting deadlines is just as critical as producing excellent results. Moving forward, I am committed to refining my time management skills to ensure I can consistently meet deadlines while maintaining the high standards I strive for in my work.'),
(14, 247, 73, 'Sustainable Productivity Enhancement Program Leader- Crop Ecophysiologist', '2024', 'draft', '2024-12-06 09:48:25.357', '2024-12-06 09:48:25.357', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'sent', 'Commendable. \nI completed all my assignments as required.', 'Commnendable.\nI possessed the technical competencies for the position and have been instrumental in the completion of some analyses', 'I am part of the SPE team and have been collaborated on different activities with other colleagues. The collaboration has been fruitful so far  as we are finilazing some draft papers.', 'Commendable.\nI strived to be pro-active and initate some research activities (e.g., data curation and analysis, brainstorming with peers at other institutions).', 'Meet requirements.\nI always read the instructions/procedures of AfricaRice in my research activities and seek for assistance whenever required.', 'Commendable', 'Commendable.\nOver the past 6 to 7 months I consistenly demonstrated the expertise and skill expected for this position.'),
(15, 96, 27, 'Seed Unit Coordinator', '2024', 'draft', '2024-12-08 18:14:12.075', '2024-12-08 18:14:12.075', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'sent', 'Les objectifs assigns cette anne ont t atteint a 80%. En effet,\n-	O1 : Nous avons produit 13.149 tonnes de semences sur 12 tonnes prvus.\n-	O2 : Nous avons apport un appui technique aux NARS\no	Mise en place de 1.5ha de production de semences de prbase au Liberia,\no	Contribuer  la formation des NARS et acteurs du secteur priv, sur les bonnes pratiques agricoles en production de semences (du 08 au 12 juillet 2024) a Mb.\no	Mise en place de parcelles de dmonstration en collaboration avec le PADFA en milieu paysan et en station sous le projet KAFACI.\n-	O3 : Nous avons contribuer cette au renforcement de capacit de trois personnels des centres nationaux de recherche (deux soudanais et un Gambien)\n-	 O4 : les grosses pluies de cette anne nont pas permis de mettre en place les parcelles de production de semences de prbase a temps. Toutefois nous avons commenc la production de semences prbase de 4 lignes upland et des varits NERICA L19, NERICA L20 et NERICAL19Sub1. \n', 'Nous disposons les comptences techniques requises en matire de production de semences.', 'Au cours de cette anne, nous avons faire montre dun engagement total pour conduire a bien les activits et atteindre les objectifs.', 'Nous avons toujours pris des initiatives pour lavancement des activits de production de semences,  travers le prfinancement de certaines activits en station et de certaines missions. Faire des propositions qui contribuent  amliorer le travail', 'Nous avons respect la plupart des instructions donnes dans le cadre des activits ralises cette anne. ', NULL, 'De faon gnrale, nous sommes satisfaits des activits ralises et les objectifs atteints au cours de cette 2024, malgr les difficults et les dfis auxquels nous avons faire face. Toutefois, nous pouvons faire encore mieux pour atteindre de plus grands rsultats et tre encore plus performant.'),
(16, 233, 20, 'Policy, Innovation Systmes And Impact Assessment Program Leader-impact Assessment Economist', '2024', 'draft', '2024-12-09 04:59:25.715', '2024-12-09 04:59:25.715', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'sent', 'I\'ve been about 70% efficient regarding my set objectives. My involvement in writing of the CGIAR Science Program on Better Diets and Nutrition took up quite a bit of my time. ', 'I\'ve ventured into a new area of research on understanding how markets impact diets, and not just the consumption of single food commodities. I\'m at the early stages of developing my expertise in modeling the relations between markets and diets in food environment and food system frameworks.', 'As always, I\'ve remained committed to the core mandate of AfricaRice. With the support of AfricaRice management, I have, in my capacity as the Country Representative for Uganda, succeded in getting IITA to accept to host AfricaRice in Uganda. This is a big step towards strengthening the AfricaRice program in East Africa.', 'I initiatied the enrolment of a PhD student - Morish Obura - on the Multiple Harvest Rice for Africa Project in Uganda. He is under the supervision of the project coordinator, Dr. Elliott Dossou-Yovo. ', 'I have remained consistent with my ability to follow instructions from management and the teams with whom I work. I consider this attribute to be critical to achieving common goals and the Center\'s ambitions.', 'I have ably co-led the Market Intelligence Initiative at AfricaRice and the Center\'s activities and relations in Uganda. ', 'Overall, I have remained steafast in my technical work and in promoting the presence and visibility of AfricaRice in the East African region. I also appreciate my involvement in and contribution to projects being coordinated by my colleagues in other AfricaRice programs.'),
