(201, 214, 135, 'Director General', '2025', 'draft', '2025-03-28 16:11:26.778', '2025-03-28 16:11:26.778', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'sent', 'I carry out the tasks assigned to me with efficiency, seriousness, and speed, while respecting deadlines in an exemplary manner. As a personal assistant, I have accomplished the following:\n\nCalendar Management: Planning and coordinating the DG\'s appointments and engagements to optimize his schedule.\nTravel Organization: Preparing travel itineraries, booking tickets and accommodations, and managing logistical details in coordination with the travel service, protocol, and communication departments.\nCommunication: Drafting and managing correspondence, including emails, letters, and mission reports.\nGuest Reception: Coordinating internal and external visits, welcoming guests, and preparing meetings.\nAdministrative Support: Preparing necessary documents for meetings and presentations, and managing files and archives.', 'Here are some technical skills that have helped me achieve my objectives:\n	Time Management: Ability to plan and organize tasks assigned by the DG effectively, prioritizing activities and meeting deadlines.\n	Communication Skills: Excellent written and oral communication skills, including drafting letters, reports, and emails, as well as the ability to communicate clearly and professionally with various stakeholders and partners of the organization.\n5.	Discretion and Confidentiality: Ability to handle sensitive and confidential information with discretion and integrity.\n6.	Versatility and Adaptability: Ability to adapt to changing situations and manage multiple tasks simultaneously.\n7.	Interpersonal Skills: Aptitude to establish and maintain positive working relationships with colleagues,  and external partners.\n8.	Problem Solving: Ability to identify and resolve problems proactively and effectively.\n9.	Stress Management: Ability to work under pressure and manage stress constructively.', 'I am highly committed to executing my tasks, which is reflected in the following:\n1.	Dedication: I demonstrate dedication to my responsibilities and tasks, putting in every effort to achieve the set objectives.\n2.	Reliability: I am someone my colleagues and superiors can rely on, consistently meeting deadlines and delivering high-quality work.\n3.	Proactivity: I take the initiative in drafting verbal notes and other correspondence, anticipating the needs of the DG\'s office, including purchases and proposals to the DG.\n4.	Passion: I am passionate about my work, which is evident in the enthusiasm and constant motivation I bring to my role.\n5.	Collaboration: I work effectively in a team with the assistant and other administrative assistants, contributing to a positive and productive work environment.\nFinally, all tasks assigned by my supervisor have been completed.\n', 'Proactivit : J\'ai lu les recommandations du 33me Comit et slectionn les parties concernant les actions du DG. J\'ai pris l\'initiative de les lui rappeler. De plus, je coordonne actuellement avec le service protocole pour entrer en contact avec les ambassades des pays du Golfe Persique.\nInnovation : J\'ai apport de nouvelles ides visant  renouveler la salle de confrence du DGO en imprimant la vision sur un kakemono afin d\'imprimer dans l\'esprit des visiteurs la vision d\'AfricaRice.\nLeadership : Je dmontre des qualits de leadership en prenant en charge l\'organisation des afterworks pour le bus qui me conduit au travail, et mes collgues sont trs satisfaits.\nAmlioration continue : Je cherche toujours  amliorer mes comptences, mes connaissances et mes performances en prenant en compte les observations du DG, en observant son attitude, son type de leadership et sa grande humilit.', 'I have always committed to following the instructions and procedures given to me in order to better execute my tasks by:\n1.	Paying attention to detail.\n2.	Carefully reviewing instructions and procedures to ensure accuracy and completeness in task execution.\n3.	Systematically following instructions and procedures to establish trust and dependability with my supervisor.\n4.	Adjusting to new procedures and instructions as needed, demonstrating flexibility and a willingness to learn.\n', 'Regarding my sense of leadership, I have a clear vision in setting my objectives, and I constantly feel inspired to give my best. I communicate clearly with my supervisor and the assistant in Abidjan. I quickly understand my supervisor\'s needs. I am honest, demonstrate integrity, and maintain ethical and consistent behavior in my actions and decisions, building trust and respect. Finally, I encourage continuous learning and development.', 'I wish to express my profound gratitude to my supervisor  for his availability, invaluable support, and precious knowledge, which have enabled me to achieve my objectives. I also warmly thank certain colleagues for their collaboration and the team spirit displayed during Science Week.\n\nFinally, I thank Almighty God for AfricaRice, which has given me the opportunity to modestly contribute to the development of the organization. The year 2024 has been remarkable, and I have been able to achieve my goals thanks to this synergy.\n\nI am determined to face all the challenges that will come my way in the upcoming year 2025, already underway, with God\'s grace.'),
