(213, 265, 263, 'Seed Value Chain Consultant and Country Representative for Liberia', '2025', 'draft', '2025-03-30 21:25:13.237', '2025-03-30 21:25:13.237', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'sent', 'I effectively managed my time and resources to consistently meet project deadlines, even when dealing with unforeseen challenges such as iron toxicity and land availability constraints. I developed structured work plans to ensure smooth execution of activities.', 'I demonstrated strong expertise in breeder seed production, business planning, and stakeholder engagement. My ability to apply climate-smart agronomic practices helped improve production outcomes. Additionally, I conducted on-site training for CARI staff to enhance their skills.', 'I remained fully engaged and available for project activities, proactively addressing bottlenecks and ensuring that targets were met. My dedication to the success of the Seeds4Liberia project is reflected in the successful production of breeder seeds and stakeholder engagement efforts.', 'I led efforts to identify and resolve key project challenges, including managing iron toxicity in breeder seed fields through improved drainage techniques. My proactive problem-solving ensured the project stayed aligned with its goals and timelines.', 'I strictly followed project protocols, ensuring compliance with AfricaRice and EU regulations. My work adhered to best practices in seed production and project management.', 'I provided technical guidance and mentorship to CARI staff, ensuring that they understood best practices in seed production.\n', 'I consistently meet deadlines by managing my time and priorities. My strong technical skills and proactive approach help me solve problems and improve continuously. I always follow procedures and am committed to my responsibilities'),
