(254, 151, 244, 'High-altitude Rice Breeder', '2024', 'sent', '2025-04-24 08:56:13.394', '2025-04-24 08:56:13.394', 'Staff achieved the goal and even surpassed the expectation.', 5, 'Great technical showcase.', 5, 'The staff has shown great committment for continous improvement.', 5, 'Great initiative and follow through. ', 5, 'Staff have shown commendable compliance and coordination that secured Long-Term Grant.', 5, 'Excellent leadership quality demonstrated.', 5, 'Excellent overall achievement!', 5, 'sent', 'I consistently delivered high-impact outcomes across all genebank objectives in 2024. I ensured that all targetsseed availability, safety duplication, data management, and regenerationwere not only met but surpassed. My ability to streamline genebank operations, implement innovations (e.g., Videometer, GGCE), and successfully coordinate reviews and funding reports reflects unmatched efficiency in a high-stakes environment', 'I demonstrated exceptional leadership by guiding cross-functional teams through complex projects such as the external review, GGCE migration, and pangenome development. My leadership drove collaboration across CGIAR centers and national genebanks, positioning AfricaRice as a continental hub for genebank excellence. The successful training sessions, proposal writing, and strategic partnerships are a testament to my vision, technical strength, and capacity to mobilize resources and people.\n________________________________________\n', 'My unwavering commitment to the mission of AfricaRice is evident through my sustained efforts to modernize infrastructure, improve operational sustainability, and enhance visibility of the genebank globally. I ensured continuous staff development, donor engagement, and proactive responses to stakeholder needs. My hands-on involvement in every stagefrom technical upgrades to strategic planningdemonstrates a deep and ongoing dedication to excellence and service.\n________________________________________\n', 'I 