(138, 'ok', '2024', 104, 92, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2024-07-31 09:09:08.769', '2024-07-31 09:09:08.769', NULL, '1.	Spicework Report', 'Monthly report of tasks and activities recorded on the Spicework platform.', 'All requests for assistance and support must be entered on the Spicework platform via the user portal.', '2024-12-31', 'Regular reporting at the end of each month.', 4, 'La mis en oeuvre de spicework est effective. Les rapports sont produits regulirement comme convenu.', 'Report well followed and sent to  team, completed objective.', 'SpiceWorks reporting is done monthly.', ''),
(139, 'ok', '2024', 166, 64, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2024-07-31 11:24:01.432', '2024-07-31 11:24:01.432', NULL, 'Review of Stations\' financial reports', 'Review monthly financial reports and justifications of stations to ensure accuracy, completeness, timeliness, and adherence to AfricaRice Financial Management Guidelines, and assess internal control procedures.', 'The monthly financial reports/justifications of stations are accurate, complete, timely, and compliant with AfricaRice Financial Management Guidelines.', '2024-12-31', '1. Accuracy (99% error-free transactions)\n2. Completeness (100% complete and reconciled accounts)\n3. Timeliness (100% reports submitted on time)\n4. Reporting of Potential Breaches (100% reported within timeframe)\n', 4, 'This has been well done with frequent feedback and guidance given to the outstation accountants ', 'I have effectively managed and prioritized tasks to achieve 100% review completion of 2024 financial reports, showcasing my ability to work efficiently under pressure. Rating: 5/5.', NULL, ''),
(140, 'ok', '2024', 166, 64, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2024-07-31 11:26:51.753', '2024-07-31 11:26:51.753', NULL, 'Cash and Bank Reconciliations', 'To conduct monthly analysis and reconciliation of balance sheet accounts, cash/bank imprest accounts, and HQ cash and bank accounts, and provide support to HQ-Team in finance operations, accounting, and donor reporting.', 'The monthly analysis and reconciliation of balance sheet accounts, cash/bank imprest accounts, and HQ cash and bank accounts are accurate, timely, and effective, and the support provided to the HQ-Team in finance operations, accounting, and donor reporting is of high quality and meets their needs.', '2024-12-31', '1. Accurate and timely reconciliation of balance sheet accounts (100%)\n2. Cash/bank imprest account reconciliation accuracy (100%)\n3. HQ cash and bank account reconciliation accuracy (100%)\n4. Timely response to HQ-Team support requests (100%)\n5. Error-free accounting and finance operations support (100%)\n', 3, 'This has been done with some delays noted on the bank reconciliations.', 'In 2024, I have proactively identified and resolved discrepancies in monthly bank statements, demonstrating strong attention to detail and commitment to financial accuracy. Despite occasional delays due to external factors, such as late submission of bank statements from HQ or Stations, I have maintained a high level of quality in my work. Rating: 4/5', NULL, NULL),
(141, 'ok', '2024', 166, 64, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2024-07-31 11:33:10.123', '2024-07-31 11:33:10.123', NULL, 'Stations\' Funds Replenishment Request', 'To conduct a review of the cash projections submitted by Field Stations and to process the replenishment of funds in accordance with the budget approved by PBU and DFCS once the Month-End Accounts are finalized. The goal is to ensure that the funds are replenished promptly and in accordance with the approved budget.', 'This is to ensure timely, efficient, and compliant management of cash projections and fund replenishment requests, aligning with approved budgets and facilitating swift replenishment of funds.', '2024-12-31', '1. Timely review of cash projections (100% within 2 days)\n2. Efficient facilitation of fund replenishment requests after PBMs budget clearance. (100% within 5 days)\n', 4, 'The Outstations always receive their funds promptly, there is active engagement with PBU to obtain budget clearance.', 'I have demonstrated strong attention to detail in reviewing fund requests, ensuring alignment with approved budgets and prompt release of funds to the Stations.  Rating 5/5.', NULL, NULL),
(142, 'ok', '2024', 166, 64, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2024-07-31 11:34:56.703', '2024-07-31 11:34:56.703', NULL, 'Deployment of OCS to Outstations', 'In conjunction with ICT, this objective is to ensure the deployment and full operational status of OCS system in the Stations - Senegal, Madagascar and Nigeria by the end of the 3rd quarter. This will involve comprehensive staff training, seamless integration with existing processes, and rigorous testing. .', 'This is to ensure that the deployment of the OCS system is successful, efficient, and effective in enhancing financial and operational capabilities.', '2024-12-31', '1. Deployment Timeline: 100% of OCS system deployment in each station (Senegal, Madagascar, and Nigeria) by the end of Q3.\n2. Staff Training: 100% of relevant staff trained by August 31st.\n3. Integration and Testing: 100% resolution of integration issues identified by September 15th.\n', 3, 'The accountant has persisted in her efforts to have the Outstations record their transactions in OCS, this is still ongoing.', 'OCS implementation is progressing well, with St. Louis and Madagascar now fully deployed. We are on track to complete the rollout to AfricaRice Dakar - Hosted Organizations by Q2 2025, thanks to collaborative efforts with colleagues. I will continue to liaise with stakeholders to ensure timely completion. Rating 4/5.', NULL, NULL),
(143, 'ok', '2024', 166, 64, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2024-07-31 11:37:23.975', '2024-07-31 11:37:23.975', NULL, 'NARS advances/justifications', 'To review NARs advances and accruals for liquidation/justification and confirming their proper recording in the system before initiating subsequent payments.  ', 'This is to ensure that advances and accruals are accurately recorded, justified, and processed in the system before payments are executed, guaranteeing proper accountability and minimizing errors.', '2024-12-31', '100% Accuracy of Recording.', 3, 'The accountant has diligently ensured that partners do not receive additional advances without justification of previous advances.', 'Throughout 2024, I maintained exceptional financial management standards, accurately recording and processing advances and accruals, minimizing errors, and enhancing accountability. Rating: 5/5', NULL, NULL),
