(196, 'ok', '2024', 80, 60, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-08-08 15:11:20.234', '2024-08-08 15:11:20.234', NULL, 'Objective 3', ' Supervise lab staff and field staff for above two objectives (1 and 2).\n', 'Be able to manage both teams (Laboratory and Field staff) effectively\n', '2024-12-31', 'All activities in the laboratory and field must be carried out within the agreed timeframe.\n', 5, 'That is great. Effective management of the team is key to ensure the quality of the results. Besides, the initiative of recruiting a lab technician needs to be encouraged. ', 'Supervision of my team in the laboratory and in the field is going very well.\nAll planned activities are carried out in a spirit of teamwork and collaboration.\nTo strengthen our operational capacity, we recruited a laboratory technician.\n\n', 'Supervision of my team in the laboratory and in the field is going very well.\nAll planned activities are carried out in a spirit of teamwork and collaboration.\n', ''),
