(198, 'ok', '2024', 80, 60, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-08-08 15:18:47.444', '2024-08-08 15:18:47.444', NULL, 'Objective 5', ' Contribute to the identification of the center risk in the soil laboratory and mitigation strategies.\n', 'Comply with all safety measures relating to the use of equipment and chemicals in the laboratory\n', '2024-12-31', 'Good use of laboratory equipments and chemicals\n', 5, 'That is excellent to maintain safety measures in the lab given the sensitity of the chemicals. It is a good practice to have the trained staff use coat, gloves and have exincters in the lab. ', 'We actively participated in the center\'s risk management of laboratory work in accordance with AfricaRice procedures.\nWe placed extinguishers inside and outside the laboratory to secure staff and laboratory equipment, as we use very sensitive chemicals and equipment in the laboratory. \nAll laboratory staff were trained in the use of the extinguishers.\nWe have a risk management aspect to laboratory work; for example, all reagents were managed on hote. Manipulators must wear closed shoes, coat, gloves, and protective glasses during manipulation.\n', 'We actively participated in the center\'s risk management of laboratory work in accordance with AfricaRice procedures.', ''),
