(209, 'ok', '2024', 165, 217, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-08-09 10:38:54.000', '2024-08-09 10:38:54.000', NULL, 'Upland breeding trialing', 'Implementation of mechanized OYT, AYT and MET upland breeding trials to access the higher yield potential and wider adaptability traits under dry direct seeded conditions', '- Prepare land and provide irrigation on time\n- Apply fertilizer on time and well manage weed control\n- Properly collect data according to the protocol\n', '2024-12-31', '- DSR trials seeded using machine seeder on time\n- Fertilizer and herbicide applied \n- Data collected according to the protocol', 5, 'Done excellent job in handing these upland breeding trials and submitted data in EBS.', 'The upland DSR trials: OYT, ATYs, and MET conducted during the dry and wet seasons have been successfully completed, and the data collected is currently under analysis by the biometrician.', 'The experiments (OYT, AYT and MET) planned for 2024 in both dry and the wet seasons were successfully sown using the Wintersteiger dry direct seeder. Basic fertilisers and urea were applied on time as required, based on the results of soil analyses to access lines higher yield potential and wider adaptability traits.', ''),
(210, 'ok', '2024', 165, 217, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-08-09 10:58:47.161', '2024-08-09 10:58:47.161', NULL, 'Supervision of research technicians ', 'Supervise technicians during trial implementation and data collection to ensure compliance with experimental protocols and the reliability of the data collected.', '- Have tablets and other tools\n- Pecific training\n ', '2024-12-31', '- SOP in french given to research technicians as a guide for they activities\n- Short meeting organised daily for the activities update \n- Data collected checked daily', 4, 'He  has done very  goodjob in handling the technicians and provided guidnce to them  in capturing data precisely.', 'I provided daily supervision to the research technicians and offered additional training to enhance their skills, ensuring the collection of high-quality data.', 'At the start of the season, I gave training to the technicians on how to successfully manage a trial and how to collect agronomic data. I also held regular meetings with them at the beginning of each week to take stock of what had already been done and what still needed to be done in order to make any updates.', ''),
(211, 'ok', '2024', 224, 217, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-08-09 11:03:43.472', '2024-08-09 11:03:43.472', NULL, 'Hybridization ', 'Establish and execute a systematic crossing plan, overseeing the management of the crossing block to ensure timely and accurate execution of designed crosses, thereby optimizing breeding efforts', 'Ensure that 98-100% of the crosses are performed correctly according to the crossing plan (e.g., correct parental lines, no cross contamination)', '2024-12-31', 'Percentage of crosses executed accurately as per the design specifications', 5, 'He has sufficiently acchieved this task and produced the required number of F1 seeds from the 2024 crosses designed in all the breeding pipleines.', 'The task has been successfully completed ahead of schedule with 100% of the crosses correctly performed according to the crossing plan', 'Studies have been created in the Enterprise Breeding System (EBS) for all the breeding pipeline. Parents for each ecology have been seeded at four successive weeks. Crop management ', ''),
(212, 'ok', '2024', 224, 217, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-08-09 11:03:46.480', '2024-08-09 11:03:46.480', NULL, 'Rapid generation advancement Facility', 'Efficiently manage F1 to F5 nurseries in both field and RGA facilities on a daily basis, ensuring optimal growth conditions and thorough data collection to support breeding program advancements', 'Successfully advance a high percentage of lines from the nursery stage to further breeding trials or stages', '2024-12-31', 'Percentage of plants that successfully progress from one generation to the next ', 5, 'He has maintained very well the rapid generation adavancement fascility of Africarice and a significant number of lines has been forwarded under this fascility.', 'Successful advancement of lines from F2 to F5 for all the breeding pipelines. ', 'Advancement of population for all the breeding pipeline ( Irrigated lowland, Rainfed lowland, rainfed upland and high elevation) are in progress. All the population are in the 2nd cycle and the final cycle will be completed by the end of the schedule time', ''),
