(227, 'ok', '2024', 132, 244, 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-08-12 11:07:38.357', '2024-08-12 11:07:38.357', NULL, '2.	Testing, Trailing and Data-driven decisions of ', '	Establishing OYT and MET trails  Rainfed Lowland and Irrigated.\n	Data collection\n	Sampling for grain quality and pathology tests\n	Data management and submission', '	Recruitment of a field technician or Field Observer,\n	Received seeds of OYT and MET Rainfed lowland and Irrigated from principal breeders at time,\n	Buy envelops for sampling grain for grain quality and pathology tests\n	Farm manager should prepare the land at time\n	Funds for hiring daily hand labors\n', '2024-12-31', '	A report of the recruitment process\n	Data of the OYT and MET rainfed lowand and Irrigated are available: field selection of  181 /957 from  OYT-I  and 13/45 Form MET-I;  field selection of 114/762 lines from OYT -R and 20/55 lines from MET -R\n	Results of grain quality test of OYT-R, OYT -I, MET -R and MET -I  are not yet available\n-Results of Pathology test of OYT-R, OYT -I, MET -R and MET -I  are not yet available\n\n', 4, 'Excellent support to breeders in on-station trials, however the quality needs to be enhanced as heritability is very low for traits that should not be the case.', '', '-957 lines from OYT irrigated were seeded on 23/09/2024 and transplanted 21 days later using P-Rep design; \n-762 lines from OYT rainfed lowland were seeded on 30/03/2024 and transplanted on 20/04/2024 using P-Rep design ; \n-45 lines from MET  irrigated were seeded on 05/06/2024 and transplaned on 26/06/2024 using Alpha lattice design; \n-55 lines from Rainfed lowland were seeded on 06/06/2024 and transplanted on 27/06/2024 using Alpha Lattice design; \n-', ''),
