(229, 'ok', '2024', 132, 244, 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-08-13 15:15:49.668', '2024-08-13 15:15:49.668', NULL, '4. Developing historical data repository of breedi', '4. Developing historical data repository of breeding trails using EBS\n	Help organizing historical data (ten years) from different breeding trails in a systematic format.\n	Ensuring the data is stored in EBS with help from Data manager.\n	Ensure accessibility of data anytime as required.\n	Create Database: With updated varietal release information from all Africa countries.', '	Database of the 10 years trials,', '2024-12-31', '	List of Varieties submitted for release per country\n	Database  of variety released per country for all Africa country\n	BTF data available in the EBS and the GDI drive\n	Data master file of the breeding trials for ten years is available\n', 4, 'The data base needs transformation and regular (at least 2x per year) follow up with the database manager to update the information and add new varietieties in coordination with breeders and NARES. ', '', '-43 Advanced lines were selected by NARES to be submited  for release in 7 countries; \n-417 varieties were released between 2009-2024 in 28 African Countries\n-All the BTF data are available in the GDI drive . the storage of th edata in EBS is on-going;\n-The Data Master of the Breeding trials from 2014-2024 is available', ''),
(230, 'ok', '2024', 132, 244, 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-08-13 15:19:29.848', '2024-08-13 15:19:29.848', NULL, '5. Research Publications, Flyers related to BTF ac', 'Write publications and other work assigned by the supervisor', 'Good research data for analysis and photos', '2024-12-31', '	Research Publications, flyers of BTF activities  and Website content  available\n', 3, 'Staff can improve the publication record either scieitific publication or preparing flyers for newly released varieties.', '', 'Manuscript\nYonnelle Dea Moukoumbi1*; Mouritala Sikirou2,3*, Julia Eudoxie Olong Obiang1, Roland Bocco4; Romaric Avou Tsoboua1; Adot Herv Gildas Akueson5; Yedomon Ange Bovys Zoclanclounon6,7; Moussa Sie8:Agronomic Performance of Advanced Double Haploid Elite Rice (Oryza sativa) Lines in Estuaire, Gabon\", submitted to Cogent Food & Agriculture (Open Research) ,. Accepted  with minor correction.\n- Mamadou Laho Barry1, Esther Pegalepo2, Roland Bocco3, Mamady Millimono1, Amoah Nana Koffi Abaka2, Sanjay Katiyar Kumar2, Baboucarr Manneh4 features me as co-author and corresponding author. Title: Screening of Advanced Rice Accessions to Increase Yield in Mangrove Agricultural Systems (submitted to Agriculture journal for review;\n-  Yonnelle Dea Moukoumbi1,2*, Raafat El-Namakay2, Mouritala Sikirou3, Roland Bocco4, Daouda Mbodj2, Esther Pegalepo5, Adot Herv Gildas Akueson6, Baboucarr Manneh2. Field Evaluation of Advanced Rice Lines to Discover Superior High Yielding; under review\n\n', ''),
