(311, 'ok', '2024', 102, 149, 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', '2024-09-17 11:52:45.496', '2024-09-17 11:52:45.496', NULL, 'Theme  de Recherche', 'Effets de la culture intercalaire riz-lgumes sur le rendement et la qualit des grains de dix nouvelles varits de plateau\nCette tude vise  tudier la performance du riz de montagne dans la zone agrocologique humide des systmes de cultures intercalaires de Cte d\'Ivoire.\nObjectifs spcifiques\n-	Dterminer le rendement, les paramtres de rendement et les proprits physicochimiques des grains du riz pluvial produit dans le systme de culture intercalaire de riziculture,\n-	Dterminer le rendement et les paramtres de rendement des cultures horticoles  gombo, pastque et courgette produits en association avec le riz\n-	valuer les avantages conomiques et nutritionnels du systme de cultures intercalaires de riziculture par rapport  la monoculture de riz.\n', NULL, '2024-12-31', '- Mise en place \n- Suivi\n- Prise de donnees', 5, 'Agree with the staff. I will say that this objective was properly performed. The staff were involved in the planning and implementation of these experiments.', 'Nous avons faitla mise en place de l\'essai ,les activites menes sont comme suit:\n-Delimitation et preparation de la parcelle\n-Semi du riz et un mois apres semis des cultures intercalaire(Gombo,courgette et pasteque)\n-irrigation et desherbage regulier des mauvaises herbes\n-fertilisation et traitements phytosanitaires appliquees\n-mise en place de la cloture autour de l\'essai pour eviter l\'attaque des rongeurs \n-Pose de filet de protection\n-prise de donnees du taux de germination des riz et les legumes\n-prise de donnees agronomiques\n-recolte et pese de rendement\n-echantillonage\n- Stockage\n- Analyses de qualite grain en cour', 'Nous avons faitla mise en place de l\'essai ,les activites menes sont comme suit:\n-Delimitation et preparation de la parcelle\n-Semi du riz et un mois apres semis des cultures intercalaire(Gombo,courgette et pasteque)\n-irrigation et desherbage regulier des mauvaises herbes\n-fertilisation et traitements phytosanitaires appliquees\n-mise en place de la cloture autour de l\'essai pour eviter l\'attaque des rongeurs \n-prise de donnees du taux de germination des riz et les legumes', 'Agree with staff.  The support provided was critical for the successful implementation of these experiment.  The both set up the fileds and manage the temporal workers.'),
(312, 'ok', '2024', 102, 149, 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', '2024-09-17 11:58:35.842', '2024-09-17 11:58:35.842', NULL, ' Gestion des echantillons', 'Faire la collecte des chantillons des marches de Cote d\'Ivoire, leur stockage et leur analyse de Qualit Grain  ', NULL, '2024-12-31', '- Nombre d\'echantillons collectes', 5, 'Agree with the staff. I will say that this objective was properly performed. The staff were involved in different grain quality analysis.', 'Nous avons receptionn 5577 echantillons de divers horizons, que nous avons stock correctement. Ce sont les echantillons en provenance de:\n\n- Departement Qualit Grain,\n\n- Selection,\n\n- Agronomie,\n\n- CNRA,\n\n- Senegal,\n\n- Ghana,\n\n- Mali, -\n\n- Nigeria,\n\n- Burkina Faso.\n- Togo\n-Liberia\n-Madagascar\n-Cameroun', 'Nous avons receptionn 3856 echantillons de divers horizons, que nous avons stock correctement. Ce sont les echantillons en provenance de:\n\n- Departement Qualit Grain,\n\n- Selection,\n\n- Agronomie,\n\n- CNRA,\n\n- Senegal,\n\n- Ghana,\n\n- Mali, -\n\n- Nigeria,\n\n- Burkina Faso.', 'We received a lot of samples for grain quality analysis in 2024 and the staff play a key role in reception, organization and analysis of the samples.'),
(313, 'ok', '2024', 102, 149, 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', '2024-09-17 12:04:09.769', '2024-09-17 12:04:09.769', NULL, 'gestion des analyse, creation de base de donnees', '  -Faire 4000 analyses au laboratoire de qualit des grains et assurer la bonne prise de donnes par les observateurs et les journaliers.\n- Creer au moins 5 bases de donnees pour les echantillons collectes et analysees', NULL, '2024-12-31', '- le nombre d\'analyse 4000\n- creation de 05 bases de donnees', 5, 'Agree with the staff. I will say that this objective was properly performed. The staff were involved in grain quality analysis and keing of data into the existing database for subsequent cleaning and processing.', ' Nous avons effectu 13718 analyses regroupant ( Le taux d\'humidit, Les peses de rendement, le dcorticage, le polissage, la sparation des grains, le taux d\'usinage, le taux de grains entiers, La forme des grains, les grains endommags, les curs blancs, la couleur des grains, Les proteines, l\'amylose, la viscosite, la temprature de glatinisation, le temps de cuisson, la capacite d\'absorption d\'eau des grains, la texture).\n\n- Nous avons cr 20 bases de donnes.', '- Nous avons effectu 5701 analyses regroupant ( Le taux d\'humidit, Les peses de rendement, le dcorticage, le polissage, la sparation des grains, le taux d\'usinage, le taux de grains entiers, La forme des grains, les grains endommags, les curs blancs, la couleur des grains, Les proteines, l\'amylose, la viscosite, la temprature de glatinisation, le temps de cuisson, la capacite d\'absorption d\'eau des grains, la texture).\n\n- Nous avons cr 8 bases de donnes.', 'We received a lot of samples for grain quality analysis in 2024 and the staff play a key role in reception, organization and analysis of the samples.'),
(314, 'ok', '2024', 102, 149, 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', '2024-09-17 12:07:21.799', '2024-09-17 12:07:21.799', NULL, 'Formations et analyses sensorielles', 'Faire 3 analyses sensorielles et conduire 3 formations en technologie post-recolte', NULL, '2024-12-31', '- 03 analyses sensorielles\n- 03 formations en technologie post-recolte', 5, 'Agree with the staff. I will say that this objective was properly performed. The staff were involved in the planning and implementation of these trainings with over 400 direct beneficiaries trained', 'Nous avons effectu differentes formations sur l\'etuvage dans differentes zones de la Cote d\'Ivoire. Ces zones de formation sont les suivantes:\n\n- Groupement de Guiembe\n\n- Groupement de Nondara\n\n- Groupement d\'Akanzakro\n\n- Groupement de Toudjan\n\n- Groupement de Tengrela\n\n- Groupement de Lataha\n\n- Groupement de Bodokro.\n- Groupe de Ghana(UNIDO)', 'Nous avons effectu differentes formations sur l\'etuvage dans differentes zones de la Cote d\'Ivoire. Ces zones de formation sont les suivantes:\n\n- Groupement de Guiembe\n\n- Groupement de Nondara\n\n- Groupement d\'Akanzakro\n\n- Groupement de Toudjan\n\n- Groupement de Tengrela\n\n- Groupement de Lataha\n\n- Groupement de Bodokro.', 'The staff partiipated is the organization and delivery of key training programs in grain quality, post-harvest and rice processing.'),
(315, 'ok', '2024', 68, 150, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2024-09-17 15:06:08.703', '2024-09-17 15:06:08.703', NULL, 'Content and communication materials production', 'Lead the development and dissemination of all communication and outreach materials such as annual report, brochures, journals, stories, videos, publications, books, manuals, articles', 'Content production planning with scientist\nAvailability of budget \n', '2024-12-31', '	Provide technical guidance for 100% of communication materials production\n	Ensure brand alignment for all communication materials production\n	All materials are produced within a reasonable timeframe to facilitate dissemination and usage at key moments of the year\n', 5, 'Excellent work has been accomplished by the Communications Unit under Francines leadership. Our events are now consistently well-branded, and both the Abidjan and Mb offices reflect this improved visual identity. I encourage Francine to extend this momentum by visiting the stations to support them in enhancing their visibility as well.\n\nDespite numerous requests and the late availability of budgets, the unit has successfully delivered tangible results in collaboration with our partners. Well done!', 'Guided technical content production and branding alignment for all events/workshop/conferences such as the visit of the US Secretary of States; Disease Surveillance Network conference; Annual science week; 33rd COM meeting; Mbe laboratories branding; TAFS-WCA annual meeting; SeedsforLiberia lunch ceremony; UNCCD Sustainable Land Management and Restoration training', NULL, NULL),
(316, 'ok', '2024', 68, 150, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2024-09-17 15:08:44.207', '2024-09-17 15:08:44.207', NULL, 'Leadership communication and external engagement ', 'Enforce AfricaRice positioning and visibility through leadership communication and external engagement events', 'Events planning with leadership', '2024-12-31', 'Support all DGs external engagement with key communication materials \nPrepare and execute with scientist AfricaRice participation at all exhibitions, fares, conferences that are approved by the management \nPromote all leadership communication at CGIAR to reinforce AfricaRice positioning \n', 5, 'Francine and her team have consistently supported all internal communications and prepared presentations and speeches for the Director General. The quality of these materials has been excellent and has effectively served their intended purpose.\n\nA remarkable highlight is the 940% growth in the DGs LinkedIn following  a significant achievement that reflects the team\'s dedication and strategic approach. Engagement levels have also increased notably.\nWell done to Francine and the entire Communications team. Your work is making a strong and visible impact!', 'Technical support was provided to DG for 100% external engagement as well as internal communication. This includes key talking points during audiences with central government in Gambia, Liberia, Madagascar, China, Ryad, Korea  opening remarks at several forums ie Africa Food Forum/KOPYA/WAFI/KAFACI/33RD COM;  media interviews; presentations for 56 & 57 BOT.\nDG LinkedIn account was managed in an effective way.\nThe account displays 28,205 impressions thus an increase of 940% compared to September 2024 when we started managing the DG account.\n', NULL, NULL);
