(338, 'ok', '2024', 28, 48, 'draft', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2024-10-16 14:55:20.283', '2024-10-16 14:55:20.283', NULL, 'EFFECTIVE MANAGEMENT OF SCIENCE WEEK MEETINGS', '-	Preparation and sending out of invitation letters \n-	Sharing of the program and concept note\n-	Preparation of folders and badges for the participants\n-	Request of cash advance from Finance for the ground arrangement\n-	Preparation of the attendance sheets for the registration of participants\n-	Follow up with ICT Unit for the preparation of the meeting rooms\n-	Ensure that participants perdiem is paid on due time\n-	Hotel booking in Bouak\n-	Follow up with Transport Unit for the pick-up/drop-off of participants \n-	Organize the Coffee break, Lunch and Dinner\n-	Rental of chairs and tents \n-	Decoration of the site when required\n-	Submission of the GEC to Finance after meetings\n', 'The aim is to have well organization of science week meetings with less complains, but the two past years, things are not going on well as I want. The previous years, the Science week was handled only by myself and my colleague Lucie and things were enough good. The time given to us to well organize is too short while the challenge is very high.', '2024-10-31', 'Achieve 90%', NULL, '', 'I am very happy with the organization of this years science week, people were happy and everything went smoothly.  I strongly encourage the Management, especially the Director of Research, for this new vision of involving more people into the science week organization.\nCongrats to everybody! Together, we are stronger!\n', NULL, NULL),
