(390, 'ok', '2024', 239, 217, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-11-20 10:17:38.280', '2024-11-20 10:17:38.280', NULL, 'Land Preparation ', 'Work with the farm manager for proper land preparation, field layout, seeding and transplanting based on experimental designs.', '100% of tasks completed as per the trial timeline to ensure alignment with experimental protocols', '2024-12-30', 'Percentage of land preparation, field layout, seeding, and transplanting activities completed within the scheduled timelines\n', 5, 'He has succesfully completed all the field operations in crossing block.', 'Land prepation, seeding and data taking for seed multiplication and LST trial were completed ahead of schedule timely', 'Land preparation for seed multiplication has been successfully completed, ensuring that the fields are well-prepared for optimal plant growth. The seeds have been carefully sown following the recommended planting density and agronomic practices to maximize germination and uniform growth. Simultaneously, preparations for the LST (Line Stage Trial) are actively ongoing.', ''),
(391, 'ok', '2024', 239, 217, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-11-20 10:20:08.888', '2024-11-20 10:20:08.888', NULL, 'Hybridization ', 'Make crosses based on the crossing design for each breeding pipeline', 'At least 90% success rate in achieving viable crosses', '2024-08-30', 'Percentage of successful crosses compared to the total number of attempted crosses as per the crossing design\n', 5, 'He has done excellent job in completing the assigned crosses in 2024.', 'All cross plan suggested by varoius breeders have been successfully completed ahead of the schedule time. ', 'All parental lines required for the planned crosses have been successfully seeded, marking the first critical step in the breeding process. With the booting phase underway, preparations for crossing will soon commence across all breeding pipelines', ''),
