(407, 'ok', '2024', 77, 151, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-12-03 12:36:58.053', '2024-12-03 12:36:58.053', NULL, 'Effective Seed Management and Storage Optimization', 'Monitor and record the moisture content and weight of all dried seed lots, ensuring accurate database entry and secure packing in barcoded aluminum foil pouches. Repositions seed lots from MTS or LTS into their designated positions based on their unique position codes.', 'All newly harvested accessions must be dried and have a moisture content value.\n\nAll envelopes removed from cold storage (LTS and MTS) must be re-weighed and repositioned according to their unique positioning code.\n', '2024-12-31', '	Monitor the moisture content, weight of all dried seed lots, measure their moisture content of the accessions and record the related information in the database and pack the dry seeds in barcoded aluminum foil pouches. \n\n	Repositioning all seed lots in barcoded aluminum foil pouches that came out from MTS or LTS according to their unique and respective position code.\n', 5, 'Karlin has shown excellent performance in maintaining high standards of post-harvest seed handling and storage organization in 2024. The following accomplishments highlight her efficiency and attention to detail:\n\nPost-Harvest Processing and Storage Repositioning:\nA total of 2,603 newly harvested accessions from 2023 were meticulously processed. This included drying, tagging with MTS labels on aluminum foil pouches, packing, weighing, and repositioning each seed lot in the MTS room based on their unique position codes. This level of organization reflects a rigorous application of standard operating procedures and data management protocols.\n\nMassive Storage Repositioning Effort:\nKarlin successfully managed the repositioning of 27,999 seed lotseach in barcoded aluminum foil pouchesfrom MTS or LTS back into their respective storage locations, maintaining their unique positional identifiers. This monumental task demonstrates her capacity to handle large-scale inventory operations with pr', '	2603  new harvested 2023 accessions were dried, their new aluminum foil was tagged with MTS labels, and the seeds have been packed, weighted and repositioned in MTS according to their unique position code in MTS room.\n\n	27999 seed lots in barcoded aluminum foil pouches that came out from MTS or LTS according to their unique and respective position code have been repositioned in MTS or LTS  according to their unique and respective position code.\n', '	Approximately 1,300 accessions harvested in 2023 were dried, labeled with new aluminum foil bearing MTS barcodes, packed, weighed, and repositioned in the Medium-Term Storage (MTS) room according to their respective position codes.\n	A total of around 14,000 seed lots in barcoded aluminum foil pouches were retrieved from MTS or LTS and subsequently repositioned in their original storage locations in MTS or LTS, following their unique and respective position codes.\n\n', ''),
