(424, 'ok', '2024', 47, 11, 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', '2024-12-04 10:22:42.361', '2024-12-04 10:22:42.361', NULL, ' Tissue sample coordination ', '1-	Coordinate shipping of sampled plant tissue including securing of all relevant documentation (phytosanitary certificate, import permit etc.)  for genotyping.\n', '1.	Ensure availability of all required materials for sampling, accurate labelling of samples, sampling at the right time and recording data for each sample. \n2.	Ensure the issuing of a phytosanitary certificate from the relevant regulatory authority, proper packaging and preservation method, labeling and documentation.\n', '2024-12-20', '1.	Number of shipments completed successfully within deadlines.\n2.	Percentage of shipments with complete and accurate documentation\n3.	Reduction in delays or errors compared to previous sampling and shipment\n4.	number of samples that meet the laboratory requirements. \n', 5, 'Objective successfully achieved.  all supporting documents were accurately procured in a timely manner. ', 'For the year 2024, 12 shipments have been successfully completed within the deadlines, with acknowledgment received from the recipients. All samples were shipped with accurate documentation and without any errors.', '-  8 shipments have been completed successfully within deadlines.\n- 100% of shipments with complete and accurate documentation\n- All the samples have been shipped on time and without errors.\n\n\n\n', 'Activities on-going as planned. Ensure that remaining samples are shipped before close of the year.'),
