(430, 'ok', '2024', 256, 27, 'draft', 'sent', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-12-04 10:31:17.577', '2024-12-04 10:31:17.577', NULL, 'Gestion du stock et redaction des rapports mensuel', 'Rdiger des rapports mensuels pour lensemble des actives de la production des semences et la mise  jour des bases de donnes sur les stocks de semence. ainsi que  les tests de germination mensuelle pour toutes les varietes en stock .', '- Avoir du staf permanent pour la gestion des stocks\n- disposer des equipements  neccaires pour les test de germination (germoire, boite de petri etc...)\n- ', '2024-12-31', '-Quantite des semences (en kg) en stock\n- Viabilite des semence ( % de germination)\n-Rapport mensuel sur les differentes activitees en cours ', NULL, 'Fatou has been providing monthly updates on stock balance and the status of seed quality of seeds in storage. This has improved the management of stocks in storage', 'La quantite de semences par categorie disponible en stock est bien connue a travers les mise en jours.\nLes tests de germination des semences en stock se font regulierement et les rapports sont disponibles.\nLes differents rapports d\'activites mensuel se font regulierement. ', 'La quantite de semences par categorie disponible en stock est bien connue a travers les mise en jours\n\nLes tests de germination des semences en stock se font regulierement et les rapports sont disponibles.\nLes differents rapports d\'activites mensuel se font regulierement.', ''),
(432, 'ok', '2024', 47, 11, 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', '2024-12-04 11:01:32.774', '2024-12-04 11:01:32.774', NULL, 'Genotyping Request Order Coordination', 'Coordinate all genotyping request orders in the OneCGIAR Service Request Portal.', '1.	All genotyping request orders are logged into the OneCGIAR Service Request Portal within the specified deadlines.\n2.	Genotyping requests are submitted without errors or missing information\n3.	Genotyping orders are processed and delivered to service providers without delays caused by coordination issues\n\n', '2024-12-20', '1.	Percentage of genotyping requests processed within the standard turnaround time \n2.	Percentage of genotyping requests submitted to service providers without errors or corrections needed\n', 4, 'Objective was achieved successfully with no issues. This allowed for a seamless run of submitted orders which guaranteed a low turnaround time. ', 'In total 12 requests in the OneCGIAR Service Request Portal have been done', 'I coordinated the genotyping requests for the Bouak station, Senegal, Madagascar, and Ghana in the OneCGIAR Service Request Portal.\n\n\n\n', 'Activities on-going as planned. Ensure timely submission of remaining orders.'),
