(434, 'ok', '2024', 47, 11, 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', '2024-12-04 11:34:11.501', '2024-12-04 11:34:11.501', NULL, 'Hybridization and Population Development ', 'Contribute to hybridization and population development activities.', '1.1.	Synchronization of parent lines to ensure successful crosses\n2.	Conduct hybridization during the optimal flowering period to ensure successful pollination.\n3.	Proper data collection and storage of data in the Enterprise Breeding System (EBS) database\n', '2024-12-20', '1.	Percentage of successful hybridizations versus total attempted.\n2.	Number of F1/F2 populations or breeding lines developed\n3.	Maintenance of detailed and error-free records of crosses, parent lines, and population data\n\n', 4, 'Collaborated well with the rest of the team to ensure successful achievement of this objective.', 'Successful generation of F1s for 75 different crosses have been completed and nursed to generate BC1F1.', 'Seeding and synchronization of parent lines for crosses is completed. Crop management and agronomic practices are ongoing.  ', 'Activities on-going as planned. Work closely with Isaac and Francis to ensure all seeds are harvested on time and stored well. '),
(435, 'ok', '2024', 47, 11, 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', '2024-12-04 11:46:43.017', '2024-12-04 11:46:43.017', NULL, 'Field Experimentation and Management ', '	Contribute to field experiments in the breeding team including field layout and establishment, management, data capture, harvesting and postharvest activities.', '1.	Proper site selection with optimal soil type, fertility, and environmental conditions for the crop\n2.	Timely application of fertilizers, irrigation, and pest/disease management strategies. And weed control \n3.	Clear definition of traits to be measured, standardized protocols for measurement and accurate and timely data collection.\n', '2024-12-20', '1.	Percentage of experiments established within the planned timeline.\n2.	Adherence to agronomic practices\n3.	Percentage of data points validated without error and adherence to data collection protocols\n', 4, 'This objective was successfully achieved and in a timely manner. ', 'The experiment has been successfully completed, including all agronomic data, phenotypic characterization, and post-harvest activities. The data have been successfully uploaded into the Enterprise Breeding System (EBS).', 'Field experiment on yield and phenotypic and genotypic characterization of breeding lines have been established. The experiment is at the vegetative and all agronomic practices have been put in place', 'Activities on-going as planned. Ensure proper maintenance of the trial and that you submit the data before we close for the year. '),
