(505, 'ok', '2024', 99, 151, 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', '2024-12-10 10:34:27.911', '2024-12-10 10:34:27.911', NULL, 'drying and blowing of newly harvested accessions', 'Ensure newly harvested accessions are dried under soon to approximately 16% moisture content, blown, and then transferred to the drying room for final drying', '	100% of harvested accessions are properly labeled.\n	The seed winnower operates efficiently without any breakdowns\n', '2024-12-31', '	Ensure 100% of newly harvested accessions are dried under soon to reach the target moisture content of 16% before final drying.\n	Complete the drying, blowing, and transfer of 100% of harvested accessions to the drying \n	Maintain 100% accurate records of moisture levels, fresh seed weight, processing dates, and transfer details for all harvested accessions in GG-CE\n', 5, 'Boris ensured that 100% of newly harvested accessions were sun-dried to the target 16% moisture content before final drying, with all drying and transfer steps completed efficiently. He maintained accurate records of moisture, weight, and processing details, all entered into the GGCE database, ensuring high-quality post-harvest handling and full seed traceability.', 'All newly harvested accessions were effectively dried under the sun to reach the target moisture content of 16% prior to final drying. The drying, blowing, and transfer processes were completed for 100% of the harvested accessions in a timely and efficient manner.\n\nComprehensive recordsincluding moisture levels, fresh seed weight, processing dates, and transfer detailswere maintained with 100% accuracy and entered into the GG-CE database. These efforts ensured high-quality post-harvest handling and full traceability of seed lots.', 'Newly harvested accessions have been properly dried under the sun to reduce moisture content to approximately 16%. Following initial drying, samples were blown to remove impurities and then transferred to the drying room for final moisture reduction. These steps were carefully followed to ensure seed quality and viability, in alignment with standard post-harvest handling protocols.', 'We would like to express our sincere appreciation to Mr. Yao Boris for his outstanding dedication and hard work. Thanks to his meticulous efforts, the payroll of casual workers has been consistently reviewed and verified every two weeks, ensuring accurate and timely compensation for all.'),
(506, 'ok', '2024', 257, 20, 'draft', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2024-12-10 11:37:13.904', '2024-12-10 11:37:13.904', NULL, 'Planififier et superviser de enqutes ', 'Planifier et superviser au moins une enqute auprs des acteurs de la chaines de valeur du riz. Il s\'agira ici de participer  l\'organisation des activits qui concourent au bon droulement de la collecte de donnes notamment, le recrutement et la formation des enquteurs et le suivi de leurs activits sur le terrain; ', '- Disponibilit des ressources \n- Conditions fovorables \n- Intrt des participants \n- Validation des questionnaire ', '2024-12-30', '- Rapport de formation des enquteurs\n- Rapport de supervision \n- Rapport de synthse des donnes', NULL, '', '- J\'ai particip  toutes les activits de collecte de donnes au Sngal et  l\'analyse des rsultats de l\'enqute de rfrence de tout les pays. ', '- Ralis les rapports de formation et de supervision de l\'enqute de rfrence \n- Ralis l\'puration des donnes et les analyse de synthse \n- Contribu  la planification des activits de collecte de donnes \n- Contribu  la raliseation du template du rapport et des interprtations des rsultats.', ''),
