(508, 'ok', '2024', 11, 244, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-12-10 11:53:05.740', '2024-12-10 11:53:05.740', NULL, 'Coordination of laboratory shared services for WCA', 'To coordinate laboratory shared services for CG-centers and partners in WCA under the BRS', '1. Good quality tissue samples are submitted for genotyping with timely data delivery. 2. Increased usage of BRS lab services.', '2024-12-31', '1. BRS lab services (genotyping/ elemental analysis) are adopted by CGIAR/NARES breeding programs in WCA by Dec 31, 2024. 2. Capacity of partners in WCA improved in tissue sampling, sample prep and related workflows by Dec 31, 2024.', 4, 'This is commendable work that involves our NARES partners to benefit from the genotyping services, however, we need to follow up NARES if they are able to use the genotyping data to advance their breeding program.', 'This objective was achieved with success. A total of 11 user enagements was completed virtually. I organized and delivered the WCA Genotyping workshop that brought together 32 participants from 15 NARES institutes. In addition to being trained in tissue sampling, sample prep, use of the OneCGIAR request portal and related workflows, these engagements have increased visibility of BRS and shared services. I served as a manager for the request portal  where I vetted all request from all CGs and partners, I reached out to customers where necessary.', 'Through virtual means, I have engaged 6 new users of the global laboratory shared service on tissues sampling, shipping protocols, different marker sets and their utility, use of the OneCGIAR service portal and the different services currently deployed. There is a planned physical training workshop planned later this year and I am both the organizer and resource person.', ''),
(509, 'ok', '2024', 11, 244, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-12-10 11:54:11.970', '2024-12-10 11:54:11.970', NULL, 'Coordination of CtEH projects', 'To coordinate CtEH projects on Improved Mechanization for DSR and Facilities Upgrade', '1. Irrigation projects are commissioned and handed over to AfricaRice. 2. All procured farm machinery received at Mbe and Saint Louis in good condition. 3. Seed processing unit in Saint Louis is operational.', '2024-12-31', '1. Irrigation projects at Mbe and Saint Louis completed by Dec 31, 2024. 2. Equipment and infrastructure necessary for mechanization of breeding operations procured by Dec 31, 2024.', 5, 'This is excellent contribution to enhance the capacity and quality of the phenotying effort.', 'All scheduled equipment procurement processes completed (arrived on station) and most machinery already in use to improve breeding operations at Mbe and Siant Louis. Irrigation projects in both stations 80% complete. Final installations being completed shortly to allow commissioning of the projects.', 'Irrigation projects in Mbe and Saint Louis progressing steadily as planned. Seed processing facility in Saint Louis on schedule and near completion. All equipment scheduled for procurement are at various stages of delivery.', ''),
