(518, 'ok', '2024', 242, 145, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2024-12-11 09:19:54.383', '2024-12-11 09:19:54.383', NULL, 'Increase the inclusion of women and youth in AVC', 'Contribute to reducing the challenges of including women and young people from agricultural/rice backgrounds or organisations', NULL, '2024-12-31', '1. Creation and strengthening of gender-based innovation platforms in Cte d\'Ivoire, Rwanda, Democratic Republic of Congo and Burundi ; \n\n2. Offer entrepreneurship and general skills training to women, young and leaders or members of farming communities or organisations ;\n\n3. To develop and foster business relationships with women and young leaders or members of farming communities or organisations ;\n\n4. Promote inclusive governance of agricultural innovation platforms.', 4, 'Several activities done to promote inclusion', 'By 2024, I expect to have achieved a good level of activity in supporting the inclusion of women and young people in agricultural value chains (AVCs). Our achievements are as follows: \n\n- 3 workshops to set up or strengthen gender-based agricultural innovation platforms: 1 in Cte d\'Ivoire, 1 in Rwanda and 1 in the DRC (128 leaders and members of 71 Professional Agricultural Organisations);\n\n- 5 capacity-building activities for women and young people in the field of agricultural entrepreneurship: 2 in Cte d\'Ivoire, 1 in Nigeria, 1 in Rwanda and 1 in DRC (197 leaders and members of 75 Professional Agricultural Organisations);\n\n- 35 business relationships with women and young leaders or members of agricultural organisations were identified and facilitated in Cte d\'Ivoire (3), Rwanda (25) and the DRC (7). \n\n- Promotion of inclusive governance through workshops to strengthen agricultural innovation platforms in Cte d\'Ivoire, Rwanda and the DRC.', NULL, NULL),
