(527, 'ok', '2024', 258, 20, 'draft', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2024-12-11 10:06:27.459', '2024-12-11 10:06:27.459', NULL, ' Suivi des demandes administratives ', 'Assurer le suivi de toutes les demandes administratives manant des partenaires et donateurs des autres centres de recherche agricole.\n\n', 'Grer les priorits au sein de l\'administration.\n', '2024-12-31', 'Gestion des demandes administratives et programmes du centre.', NULL, '', 'j\'ai contribuer a la gestion des demandes administratives et programmes du centre dans le cadre du programme :\n-Formation sur l\'valuation quantitative avance de l\'impact, Cotonou, Rpublique du Bnin\n-Atelier annuel et de synthse du TAFS-WCA 2024, Abuja, Nigeria\n\n', NULL, NULL),
(528, 'ok', '2024', 229, 20, 'draft', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2024-12-11 10:14:04.826', '2024-12-11 10:14:04.826', NULL, 'Draft a policy gap analysis report and tracker', 'Undertake extensive research and analysis to map out existing policies and gaps regarding food security and nutrition;\nIntegrate advocacy opportunities that are adapted to the African context.', '- Accurate design of a research protocol, data collection tools, and desk research;\n- Timely feedback from the national respondents;\n- Data availability.\n', '2024-06-30', 'A published policy gap analysis report and tracker', NULL, '', 'This objective was achieved 100%. However, there were time and data constraints, mainly due to insufficient feedback from respondents. The data was supplemented by extensive desk research, which, with the support of the Steering Committee, helped to finalize the report and to meet the deadline of 30 June 2024.\nPotential updates are expected from the feedback that will result from the upcoming regional consultation workshop.', NULL, NULL),
