(530, 'ok', '2024', 242, 145, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2024-12-11 10:49:26.552', '2024-12-11 10:49:26.552', NULL, 'Support activities for scaling up good innovations', 'Support activities to disseminate good practice and appropriate technologies through agricultural innovation platforms for women and young people ', NULL, '2024-12-31', '1. Farmers aware of good farming practices and technologies ;\n\n2. Diffused agricultural practices and technologies. ', 4, 'Good work to revive innovation platforms', 'During 2024, I also contributed to a certain extent to the scaling up of good practices and innovations in rice and other sectors through my interventions in TAFS-WCA. This contribution has been made through activities in Cte d\'Ivoire, Rwanda and the DRC to strengthen gender-based agricultural innovation platforms.\n- In Cte d\'Ivoire, 39 members of 18 organizations were the beneficiaries of training on technical routes and adapted varieties of tomato, pepper, eggplant, cassava and rice, fertilization, irrigation and compost production methods, and stoving with GEM.\n- In Rwanda, 40 members of 08 organizations were sensitized on available improved seed varieties, technical rice production routes, paddy conservation conditions, small mechanization (seed drill, weeding machines) and national market standards.\n- In the DRC, 49 members of 45 organizations have been taught technical rice routes.', NULL, NULL),
(531, 'ok', '2024', 258, 20, 'draft', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2024-12-11 10:50:06.955', '2024-12-11 10:50:06.955', NULL, 'Engagement et travail d\'quipe', 'Effectuer les  tches  qui rpondent pleinement aux attentes de l\'initiative du centre en matire de relation interpersonnelle, de prsentation et de ngociation.\n', 'Savoir grer des priorits.\n\n', '2024-12-31', 'Gerer des bases de donnes pertinentes  du programme.', NULL, '', '-Participation  la gestion des fournitures du programme de la semaine scientifique.\n -Assister les activits sur le terrain avec les quipes .\n-Planification des bases de donnes des participants.\n- Gestion  des listes des participants, hbergements et transport.', 'Je dois renforcer la collaboration, la communication et la motivation au sein du groupe. En crant un environnement o chacun de nous se sentira  impliqu et valoris, et maximisez le succs  du travail et de limplication de tous les membres de lquipe progressent dans leurs objectifs, favoriser une meilleure coopration, rsoudre les conflits de manire constructive et maintenir une dynamique dengagement au sein de lquipe et et en veillant  ce que tous les membres soient focaliss sur les rsultats collectifs,  et amliorer nos engagements et nos performances.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n', ''),
