(566, 'ok', '2024', 99, 151, 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', '2024-12-12 11:16:25.092', '2024-12-12 11:16:25.092', NULL, 'Bi-Weekly Payroll Review for Casual Workers.', 'Check the payroll of the casual workers every two weeks', '	Casual workers are recruited as needed.\n	The OSA system operates smoothly without any issues.\n', '2024-12-31', '	100% of payroll checks for casual workers are completed within the scheduled two-week period.\n	Resolve 100% of any payroll issues or discrepancies within 24 hours of identification.\n	Maintain 100% completeness and accuracy in payroll records, ensuring all necessary documentation is up to date\n', 5, 'We would like to express our sincere appreciation to Mr. Yao Boris for his outstanding dedication and hard work. Thanks to his meticulous efforts, the payroll of casual workers has been consistently reviewed and verified every two weeks, ensuring accurate and timely compensation for all.', 'Payroll checks for casual workers were consistently completed within the scheduled two-week period throughout the year, ensuring timely and accurate compensation. All identified payroll issues or discrepancies were resolved within 24 hours, demonstrating strong responsiveness and efficiency.\n\nAdditionally, payroll records were maintained with 100% completeness and accuracy, with all necessary documentation regularly updated and properly filed. These practices supported transparency, accountability, and effective workforce management.', 'The payroll of casual workers has been reviewed and verified every two weeks to ensure accurate and timely compensation. ', 'I would like to express our sincere appreciation to Mr. Yao Boris for his outstanding dedication and hard work. Thanks to his meticulous efforts, the payroll of casual workers has been consistently reviewed and verified every two weeks, ensuring accurate and timely compensation for all.'),
