(619, 'ok', '2024', 92, 164, 'draft', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2024-12-16 12:17:27.457', '2024-12-16 12:17:27.457', NULL, '3.	Development application for corporate', '3.	Development application for corporate and support service \n-	New platform for evaluation and Contract et administration (HR)\n-	Online service requisition for Dakar, Senegal centers (DFCS)\n-	Platform for recording time effort of staff (PBU)\n', '3.	Development application for corporate and support service \n-	New platform for evaluation and Contract et administration (HR)\n-	Online service requisition for Dakar, Senegal centers (DFCS)\n-	Platform for recording time effort of staff (PBU)\n', '2024-12-31', '3.	Development application for corporate and support service \n-	New platform for evaluation and Contract et administration (HR)\n-	Online service requisition for Dakar, Senegal centers (DFCS)\n-	Platform for recording time effort of staff (PBU)\n', 3, '', '-	New platform for evaluation and Contract et administration (HR) :\nEvaluation complete \nadministration on going\nAdministration in progress\nWe are facing delays due to a lack of resources. Three interns have been successively hired to work on the project, but each time they resign when they find employment.\n\n\n-	Online service requisition for Dakar, Senegal centers (DFCS) : \nTest and delivery Postpone, because of the lost of the resource. I am working for an alternative solution to be propose early in April \n\n-	Platform for recording time effort of staff (PBU)\nDevelopment complete an test. Awaiting PBU for roll out.', NULL, NULL),
(620, 'ok', '2024', 59, 151, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-12-16 12:38:18.668', '2024-12-16 12:38:18.668', NULL, 'Agro-morphological characterization of 1200 access', 'Manage the plants in the field to ensure the good growing of the plants of at last 1200 under characterization accessions and report the problems or issues faced in the field to the supervisor', '	The genebank nursery area is fully prepared and ready for use.\n	All 1,200 accessions have germinated successfully with no significant losses.\n	The characterization field is prepared and ready for use within the planned timeline.\n	Android tablets are configured, tested, and available for data collection.\n', '2024-12-31', '	 Break the seed dormancy according to the established protocol \n	Establish and efficiently manage the nursery to ensure healthy seedling development\n	Transplant seedlings in the field following the randomization plan with 100% compliance\n	Collect 51 agro-morphological traits for each accession with complete accuracy.\n	Ensure 100% of collected data is transferred to the research assistant for cleaning and validation.\n	 Thresh, blow, weigh, and move harvested material to the drying room on the same day of harvest.\n', 5, 'Ange Dossou Yovo demonstrated excellent performance in managing the genebank nursery area, ensuring all germinated accessions were successfully transplanted with no significant losses. The characterization field was effectively prepared, used, and data was collected on schedule. Additionally, Android tablets were configured, tested, and successfully deployed for data collection.', 'The genebank nursery area were fully prepared and  used\nAll germinated accessions was  successfully transplantred with no significant losses.\nThe characterization field were prepared, used and data were collected  within the planned timeline.\nAndroid tablets were configured, tested, and used for datacollection.', 'Field management activities have been effectively carried out t