(626, 'ok', '2024', 59, 151, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-12-16 14:47:42.646', '2024-12-16 14:47:42.646', NULL, 'Purification and agro-morphological characterizati', 'Conduct thorough purification and comprehensive agro-morphological characterization of the Oryza sativa mini core collection, comprising 600 accessions, to ensure genetic integrity and gather detailed trait data for each accession to support breeding and research programs.', '	The genebank nursery area is fully prepared and ready for use.\n	All 600 accessions have germinated successfully with no significant losses.\n	The characterization field is prepared and ready for use within the planned timeline.\n	Android tablets are configured, tested, and available for data collection.\n', '2024-12-31', '	Break the seed dormancy according to the established protocol \n	Establish and efficiently manage the nursery to ensure healthy seedling development\n	Transplant seedlings in the field following the randomization plan with 100% compliance\n	 Remove off-types from each plot to maintain the purity of accessions.\n	Collect 51 agro-morphological traits for each accession with complete accuracy.\n	Ensure 100% of collected data is transferred to the research assistant for cleaning and validation.\n Thresh, blow, weigh, and move harvested material to the drying room on the same day of harvest.\n', 5, 'Ange Dossou Yovo successfully prepared and utilized the genebank nursery area, ensuring all germinated accessions were transplanted with no significant losses. The characterization field was efficiently set up and data collection was completed within the planned timeline. Furthermore, Android tablets were configured, tested, and effectively used for data collection.', 'The genebank nursery area were fully prepared and  used\nAll germinated accessions was  successfully transplantred with no significant losses.\nThe characterization field were prepared, used and data were collected  within the planned timeline.\nAndroid tablets were configured, tested, and used for datacollection.', 'Significant progress has been made in the purification and agro-morphological characterization of the Oryza sativa minicore collection comprising 600 accessions. The activities have been conducted thoroughly to ensure genetic integrity and collect detailed trait data. This effort provides a valuable foundation for ongoing breeding and research programs aimed at improving rice varieties.', ''),
(627, 'ok', '2024', 59, 151, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-12-16 14:54:41.476', '2024-12-16 14:54:41.476', NULL, 'Post-Harvest Processing and Transfer of Harvested ', 'Ensure efficient post-harvest processing of all harvested accessions by threshing, performing the initial blowing, and transferring 100% of the accessions to the post-harvest laboratory with accurate field and harvest labels for proper tracking and further analysis.', '	All equipment is inspected and serviced on schedule, with no equipment failures due to lack of maintenance.\n	All required equipment is available and operational when needed for research activities, minimizing delays.\n	100% of accessions have germinated \n	No label  errors or missing information  on the labels \n\n', '2024-12-31', '	 Thresh and perform the initial blowing of 100% of harvested accessions.\n	Ensure 100% of harvested accessions are transferred to the post-harvest laboratory with corresponding field and harvest labels.\n\n	Achieve 100% equipment availability, ensuring all necessary tools (tablets, scales, grain counters, sprayers, hoes, machetes, and sickles) are ready for use during scheduled activities.\n	Maintain a 100% or higher functionality rate for all field and laboratory equipment, with minimal downtime for repairs.\n	Ensure that 100% of equipment repairs or replacements are completed within 48 hours of identification of issues.\n	Calibrate and validate 100% of measurement equipment (scales, grain counters) before each use to ensure accurate data collection.\n', 5, '  Ange Dossou Yovo ensured all equipment was available, inspected, and fully operational for research activities, promptly notifying any delays or missing information on labels. All harvested accessions were efficiently processed and transferred as planned.', 'All equipment were available, inspected, and operational for research activities and any delays or missing information on labels was notified.  \nAll harvested accession were nicely pro