(628, 'ok', '2024', 112, 217, 'sent', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2024-12-16 15:05:28.259', '2024-12-16 15:05:28.259', NULL, 'Post-Harvest Processing and Transfer of Harvested ', '\nEnsure efficient post-harvest processing of all harvested accessions by threshing, performing the initial blowing, and transferring 100% of the accessions to the post-harvest laboratory with accurate field and harvest labels for proper tracking and further analysis.', '\n	100% of accessions have germinated \n	No label errors or missing information on the labels \n', '2024-12-31', '	 Thresh and perform the initial blowing of 100% of harvested accessions.\n	Ensure 100% of harvested accessions are transferred to the post-harvest laboratory with corresponding field and harvest labels.\n\n', 4, 'Mr. Emmanuel efficiently carried out post-harvest processing of all harvested accessions, including thorough threshing, initial blowing, and the timely transfer of 100% of the accessions to the post-harvest laboratory. Each accession was accurately labeled with corresponding field and harvest information, ensuring proper tracking and enabling reliable downstream analysis. His efforts have reinforced the integrity and traceability of post-harvest operations.', 'Post-harvest processing of all harvested accessions was carried out efficiently, including thorough threshing, initial blowing, and the timely transfer of 100% of the accessions to the post-harvest laboratory. Each accession was accurately labeled with corresponding field and harvest information, ensuring proper tracking and enabling reliable downstream analysis. These efforts have supported the integrity and traceability of post-harvest operations.\n\n', NULL, NULL),
