(730, 'ok', '2024', 114, 227, 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', '2024-12-20 05:33:58.882', '2024-12-20 05:33:58.882', NULL, 'Entretenir les quipements et fournitures', 'Laver et dsinfecter les botes de Ptri, puis les scher et les ranger dans les armoires.\nDsinfecter les germoirs de manire hebdomadaire et respecter le calendrier annuel d\'entretien des germoirs.\nS\'assurer que l\'eau distille soit produite et utilise de manire approprie dans les germoirs.\nNettoyer et dsinfecter les germoirs chaque semaine, en suivant le calendrier annuel d\'entretien.\n', ' Disponibilit dun distillateur deau.\nDisponibilit de savon liquide et dhypochlorite de sodium (eau de Javel) pour la dsinfection.\n', '2024-12-31', 'Les botes de Petri et les germoirs sont propres et dsinfects.\nIl n\'y a pas d\'infestation fongique lors de l\'incubation des semences dans le germoir.\n\n', 5, 'Mlle Amani Jeannette a assur avec rigueur lentretien du laboratoire de viabilit, en veillant au lavage quotidien des botes de Ptri et au rangement soign du matriel, ainsi quau nettoyage et  la dsinfection hebdomadaire des germoirs, conformment au calendrier tabli.', 'Les botes de Ptri et les autres matriels du laboratoire de viabilit ont t lavs quotidiennement et soigneusement rangs dans les tiroirs. Les germoirs ont t nettoys et dsinfects chaque semaine conformment au calendrier annuel dentretien.', 'Les botes de Ptri et les autres matriels du laboratoire de viabilit ont t lavs quotidiennement et soigneusement rangs dans les tiroirs. Les germoirs ont t nettoys et dsinfects chaque semaine conformment au calendrier annuel dentretien.', 'Mlle Amani Jeannette a assur avec rigueur lentretien du laboratoire de viabilit, en veillant au lavage quotidien des botes de Ptri et au rangement soign du matriel, ainsi quau nettoyage et  la dsinfection hebdomadaire des germoirs, conformment au calendrier tabli.'),
(731, 'ok', '2024', 114, 227, 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', '2024-12-20 05:35:33.177', '2024-12-20 05:35:33.177', NULL, 'Faire le pointage des journaliers dans OSA', ' Faire le pointage quotidien des journalires prsentes au laboratoire pour le travail.\n Sassurer que chaque journalire a reu son salaire conformment au pointage fait dans OSA.\n', 'La disponibilit de demande de journaliers dans le systme OSA.', '2024-12-31', 'Le pointage quotidien des journalires a t effectu et enregistr correctement dans le systme OSA.\nToutes les journalires ont t pays sans erreur.\n', 5, 'Mlle Amani Jeannette a effectu avec srieux et prcision la saisie quotidienne des pointages des journaliers dans le systme OSA, assurant leur validation bimensuelle. Grce  son professionnalisme, aucun incident na t signal et toutes les journalires ont t correctement rmunres.', 'Les pointages des journaliers du laboratoire de viabilit ont t effectus quotidiennement dans le systme OSA avec exactitude.', 'Les pointages des journaliers du laboratoire de viabilit ont t saisis quotidiennement dans le systme OSA avec exactitude et valids  la fin de chaque quinzaine. Aucune plainte na t enregistre durant cette priode, et toutes les journalires ont t payes.', 'Mlle Amani Jeannette a effectu avec srieux et prcision la saisie quotidienne des pointages des journaliers dans le systme OSA, assurant leur validation bimensuelle. Grce  son professionnalisme, aucun incident na t signal et toutes les journalires ont t correctement rmunres.'),
(732, 'ok', '2024', 227, 151, 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', '2024-12-20 05:43:46.423', '2024-12-20 05:43:46.423', NULL, 'Preparation of seed samples for safety duplication', ' In collaboration with the database manager, update the list of accessions to be secured at SGSV, NLGRP, and the RDA Korea Genebank;\n Analyze the viability data of accessions designated for safety duplication and select those with a viability of at least 85%.\nIn collaboration with the research assistant responsible for managing the drying room and cold rooms, pack 10 g of high-viability seeds for at least 1,000 accessions for shipment to SGSV and NLGRP, and 5 g of seeds for at least 5,000 accessions for shipment to the RDA Korea Genebank.\n', 'Availability of high viable seeds for packing in aluminum foil pouches for safety duplication', '2024-12-31', 'At least 10 grams of highly viable seeds from 1,000 accessions have been prepared and shipped to the SGSV and NLGRP.\n 5 grams of highly viable seeds from 5,000 accessions have been prepared and shipped to the RDA Korea Genebank.\n', 5, 'Mr. Tia Dro has played a key role in the successful preparation and shipment of seed samples for safety duplication. He ensured that 5 grams of seed samples from 5,000 accessions were properly packed and shipped to the RDA Korea Genebank. Additionally, he oversaw the preparation of 10 grams of seed samples from 620 accessions for the NLGRP in the USA, and from 539 accessions for the SGSV in Norway. His efficiency and precision have been instrumental in securing the long-term conservation of the rice collection.', ' 5 grams of seed samples from 5,000 accessions have been prepared and shipped to the RDA Korea Genebank for safety duplication\n10 grams of seed samples from 620 accessions of the collection have been prepared for shipment to the NLGRP in the USA, and from 539 accessions for shipment to the SGSV in Norway.\n', 'By the end of June 2024, 5 grams of seed samples from 2,500 accessions had been packed in aluminum foil pouches, arranged in Integra plastic boxes, and shipped to the RDA Korea Genebank for safety duplication. The accompanying documents such as the phytosanitary certificate, non-GMO declaration, and commercial invoice were prepared and included in the seed boxes.\n', 'Mr. Tia Dro demonstrated strong organizational and technical skills by coordinating the preparation of 5 grams of seed samples from 2,500 accessions by the end of June 2024. The seeds were carefully packed in aluminum foil pouches, arranged in Integra plastic boxes, and shipped to the RDA Korea Genebank for safety duplication. He also ensured that all required documentationincluding the phytosanitary certificate, non-GMO declaration, and commercial invoicewas accurately prepared and included with the shipment. His diligence contributed to the smooth and successful execution of this critical task.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n'),
(733, 'ok', '2024', 227, 151, 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', 'sent', '2024-12-20 05:44:53.855', '2024-12-20 05:44:53.855', NULL, 'Conducting seed longevity experiments ', ' Conduct a pre-storage seed longevity study on at least 20 accessions of O. glaberrima and \nConduct a best harvest time experiment on 10 accessions of O. barthii, 20 accessions of O. glaberrima, and 20 accessions of O. sativa.\n', ' Availability of newly harvested seed lots for conducting pre-storage seed longevity and best harvest time experiments', '2024-12-31', 'At least pre-storage seed longevity experiment of 20 accessions have been completed \n Experiment to identify the best harvest times of O. sativa, O. glaberrima and O. barthii have been identified.\n', 5, 'Mr. Tia Dro has shown good scientific rigor  in implementing a seed longevity experiment involving 20 O. glaberrima accessions, with rehydrated seed packets treated with LiCl solution and subjected to weekly germination tests. In parallel, he is coordinating the harvest of seeds from 10 O. barthii, 20 O. glaberrima, and 20 O. sativa accessions at four different intervals (25, 30, 36, and 42 days after anthesis) to determine optimal harvesting time. His careful execution of these experiments contributes  to advancing knowledge on seed longevity and quality.', ' A seed longevity experiment with 20 O. glaberrima accessions is underway, with rehydrated seed packets treated with LiCl solution undergoing weekly germination tests.\n Seeds from 10 accessions of O. barthii, 20 of O. glaberrima, and 20 of O. sativa are being harvested at four intervals (25, 30, 36 and 42 days after anthesis) to determine the optimal harvesting time.\n', 'A literature review has been conducted to better understand the protocol for the accelerated ageing and longevity experiment using non-saturated LiCL solution. In addition, a trial to determine the optimal harvesting time for 10 accessions of O. barthii, 20 of O. glaberrima, and 20 of O. sativa has been established in the screenhouse.', 'Tia Dro has shown initiative  in conducting  the protocol for the accelerated ageing and longevity experiment using non-saturated LiCL solution. Furthermore, he successfully established a trial in the screenhouse to determine the optimal harvesting time for 10 accessions of O. barthii, 20 of O. glaberrima, and 20 of O. sativa. '),
