(741, 'ok', '2024', 260, 48, 'draft', 'sent', 'draft', 'sent', '2024-12-20 12:53:48.858', '2024-12-20 12:53:48.858', NULL, ' At least 2 manuscripts will be successfully submi', 'The objective is to ensure the successful submission of at least two research manuscripts to peer-reviewed journals by December 31, 2024. The targeted manuscripts include:\n\n\"Evaluating responses by ChatGPT to farmers questions on irrigated lowland rice cultivation in Nigeria\"  assessing the accuracy and relevance of AI-generated agronomic advice.\n\n\"Consistent yield performance of rice genotypes grown under irrigated conditions in wet and dry seasons in West Africa\"  analyzing the stability and productivity of rice genotypes across different seasonal conditions.\n\nThis objective entails completing research, data analysis, and manuscript preparation to meet journal standards and contribute valuable insights to the field.\n', NULL, '2024-12-31', '2 papers published in high-impact factor journals', NULL, '', 'A total of 6 papers published. Two of these publications were authored as the first author, while contributions were made to four additional papers. Among these, key publications include:\n1. https://doi.org/10.1038/s41598-024-53916-1\n2. https://doi.org/10.1016/j.fcr.2023.109231\n3. https://doi.org/10.1016/j.fcr.2024.109414\n4. https://doi.org/10.1016/j.fcr.2024.109294\n5. https://doi.org/10.1007/978-981-99-5890-0_17\n6. https://ousar.lib.okayama-u.ac.jp/66550', 'A total of 6 papers published. Two of these publications were authored as the first author, while contributions were made to four additional papers. Among these, key publications include:\n1. https://doi.org/10.1038/s41598-024-53916-1\n2. https://doi.org/10.1016/j.fcr.2023.109231\n3. https://doi.org/10.1016/j.fcr.2024.109414\n4. https://doi.org/10.1016/j.fcr.2024.109294\n5. https://doi.org/10.1007/978-981-99-5890-0_17\n6. https://ousar.lib.okayama-u.ac.jp/66550', ''),
