(943, 'ok', '2024', 60, 73, 'draft', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2025-03-26 16:28:20.712', '2025-03-26 16:28:20.712', NULL, 'A minimum of 3 papers published ', 'Publish a minimum of three papers in internationally peer-reviewed journals.', 'Timely review of the papers by journals ', '2024-12-31', 'A minimum of 3 papers published in international, peer reviewed \n and high impact factor journals. ', NULL, '', 'I published ten papers in 2024, including two papers as the lead author and 8 papers as co-author. The DOIs of the papers are listed below. \n1.	https://doi.org/10.1080/14735903.2024.2423595 \n2.	https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2638-8774 \n3.	https://doi.org/10.1016/j.fcr.2024.109519 \n4.	https://doi.org/10.1016/j.cliser.2024.100507\n5.	https://doi.org/10.1007/s10705-024-10360-x\n6.	https://doi.org/10.1016/j.fcr.2024.109414\n7.	doi:10.1007/s40808-024-02047-7\n8.	DOI: 10.1038/s43016-024-00936-9 \n9.	https://doi.org/10.1016/j.fcr.2024.109294\n10.	https://doi.org/10.1016/j.atech.2023.100392 \n', NULL, NULL),
(944, 'ok', '2024', 60, 73, 'draft', 'sent', 'draft', 'draft', '2025-03-26 16:29:48.093', '2025-03-26 16:29:48.093', NULL, 'A minimum of two proposals submitted ', 'Submit one proposal as the lead scientist and contribute to the development of another proposal. ', 'Availability of calls for proposals', '2024-12-31', 'Number of proposals submitted ', NULL, '', 'In 2024, I submitted 7 proposals including 6 proposals as lead and one concept note as contributor. The details are provided below. \n1.	Strengthening Resilience to Climate Change of Rice Value Chains in West Africa. 9.4 million. Approved. \n2.	AICCRA additional funding. 1.6 million USD. Approved.  \n3.	Land Restoration in Lowlands-based Systems in Africa. 100000 USD. Approved. \n4.	Scaling Gender-Equitable System of Rice Intensification (SRI) in Mali. 121,223 USD. Approved. \n5.	Mitigating Greenhouse Gas Emissions in Rice Value Chains in West Africa. 15 million USD. Under review. \n6.	Carbon Offsetting Rice Emissions. 0.56 million euro. Under review. \n7.	Enhancing Sustainable Land Management and Climate-Resilient Agri-food Systems in Cte d\'Ivoire (LARACI). 50 million USD. Under review. \n', NULL, NULL),
